    name: MIT

    post:
      summary: schema with examples
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:    
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/schema1"

        default:
          description: ok
components:
  schemas:
    schema1:
      type: 
        - object
      properties:
        objectType:
          type: 
            - integer
            - string
          examples:
            - 1234
            - 'This is an string as example'
